OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy with some rain in
OL,7,Fthe southwest and parts of Wales and
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, edging slowly
OL,9,Fnortheastwards. Otherwise a dry and
OL,10,Fclear night. Chilly in the east and
OL,11,Fnortheast. A mild night in the south
OL,12,Fand west.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FShowers in the west and
OL,15,Fsouthwest will spread northeastwards.
OL,16,FTurning heavy in places with some
OL,17,Fthundery bursts. Feeling much warmer
OL,18,Fin the east with some sunshine.
OL,19,FFeeling humid for many.
